==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|accrētiō}}, from {{m|la|ad||to}} + {{m|la|crēscō||grow}}. First attested in the 1610s. Compare {{m|en|crescent}}, {{m|en|increase}}, {{m|en|accrue}}, and so on.

